Class LecturesListAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.widget.BaseAdapter
      • de.tum.in.tumcampus.adapters.LecturesListAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.widget.Adapter, android.widget.ListAdapter, android.widget.SpinnerAdapter, se.emilsjolander.stickylistheaders.StickyListHeadersAdapter

    public class LecturesListAdapter
extends android.widget.BaseAdapter
implements se.emilsjolander.stickylistheaders.StickyListHeadersAdapter
    This class handles the view output of the results for finding lectures via TUMOnline used in LecturesPersonalActivity and ChatRoomsSearchActivity. It implements StickyListHeadersAdapter to show semester info as sticky header.
